---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---
<ContentLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Reach out to collaborate, request resources, or share feedback with the Salafi Science Network team."
  category="Get in touch"
>
  <p>
    We welcome correspondence from communities, masajid, and students of knowledge. Whether you require tailored lesson
    plans, wish to collaborate on translations, or have a question about our resources, the team will respond as soon as
    possible.
  </p>
  <h2>Email</h2>
  <p>
    <a href="mailto:contact@salafisciencenetwork.org">contact@salafisciencenetwork.org</a>
  </p>
  <h2>Contribution requests</h2>
  <p>
    If you are a student of knowledge or translator keen to contribute, please include:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your background in Islamic studies and teachers with whom you have studied.</li>
    <li>The type of content you would like to submit (article, lesson, audio, etc.).</li>
    <li>Preferred language pair if submitting translations.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Community support</h2>
  <p>
    Communities seeking structured programs or weekend school material may outline their needs so we can provide the most
    relevant resources. We aim to support masajid and institutes with authentic, classroom-ready material rooted in the
    methodology of the Salaf.
  </p>
</ContentLayout>
